08:14.282 --> 08:16.104
A lot of them were... It's a book plate.

08:16.124 --> 08:19.508
It is a book plate.

08:19.528 --> 08:19.929
Can you read it?

08:20.490 --> 08:29.121
Book collection of somebody, Elkin.

